### Model status catalog
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/models/status

### Demo safety rules
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/models/demo-safety

### Phone disease smoke route
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/detect/image
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="source_type"

phone_rgb
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample.jpg
--boundary--

### UAV crop-object smoke route, not disease
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/detect/image
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="source_type"

uav_rgb
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample.jpg
--boundary--

### UAV BLB disease smoke route
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/detect/image
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="source_type"

uav_multispectral
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="model_hint"

uav_blb
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="target_type"

disease
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="blb_preview.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./blb_preview.jpg
--boundary--
